Error: Error: "PHP Extension Required: Zip" When Trying To Install A Modpack On A Pterodactyl Minecraft Server.

Solution: 1. Log in to your server via SSH or use the Pterodactyl file manager.
2. Run the following command: `sudo apt-get install php-zip` and enter your password if prompted.
3. Once the installation is complete, restart your Apache server with the command `sudo service apache2 restart`.
4. Restart your Pterod
